For the json resource export added in 13.2, some of the values (namely `urls`, `environment` and `properties` are exported as arrays of objects, each of which have a `key` and `value properties:

Should
```jsonc
  "urls": [
    {
      "name": "grpc",
      "url": "https://otel-promtest.dev.localhost:53029/"
    },
    // etc.
  ]
```

These could be emitted as dictionaries instead:
```jsonc
